HEADWORD: Rompish
<hw>Romp"ish</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Given to rude play; inclined to
romp; frolicsome.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p>--- <wordforms><wf>Romp"ish</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos> --
